# ── Experiment outputs ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 생성된 시각화·학습 곡선·plot (각 챕터)
# Ch1: Patch=Conv 등가 검증 · CLS vs GAP · PE 비교 · inductive bias ablation
# Ch2: DeiT distillation · Swin window vs ViT global · PVT pyramid feature · CvT/CoAtNet 비교
# Ch3: SimCLR/MoCo InfoNCE 곡선 · BYOL/SimSiam stop-grad ablation · MI bound tightness
# Ch4: DINO attention map · k-NN linear probe · DINOv2 multi-objective 기여도
# Ch5: MAE 75% mask reconstruction · BEiT dVAE token · SimMIM 비교 · MaskFeat/MVP target
# Ch6: CLIP zero-shot accuracy · BLIP caption · LLaVA instruction · Flamingo few-shot
# Ch7: NeRF rendering · 3D-GS · TimeSformer / VideoMAE · scaling law plot
*.png
*.jpg
*.jpeg
*.svg
*.pdf
*.gif
*.mp4
*.webm
*.webp

# 생성된 sample / 시각화
